column1: #Text=Wikinews interviews Peter Coti , eyewitness to north eastern US storm
#Text=Mike Morales interviews fellow Wikinews contributor Peter Coti , who is on the scene at a north eastern storm in the United States in New Jersey .
#Text=Coti tells Wikinews what happened in the area of Ridgewood , New Jersey and provided pictures of the damage and area .
#Text=( ( Mike Morales ) ) Could you explain the circumstances of the incident ?
#Text=( ( Peter Coti ) ) Well on the morning of Saturday it was a normal storm .
#Text=Bit windier then a normal one though .
#Text=Then at 4:30 EST ( local time ) power went out because of a downed tree .
#Text=When I got home it was like war of the worlds .
#Text=And White , Red and blue explosions of transformers .
#Text=( ( MM ) ) Do you know which areas are affected ?
#Text=( ( PC ) ) All of ridgewoo NJ [ sic , Ridgewood , New Jersey ] .
#Text=Actually according to many people Bergan County was affected ; ALL of it and southern parts of New York .
#Text=( ( MM ) ) Besides trees , what other damage occurred ?
#Text=( ( PC ) ) Well , signs are on 45 degree angles , but trees are blocking roads and there are powerlines in [ half ] .
#Text=( ( MM ) ) Are there any damages to buildings ?
#Text=( ( PC ) ) Not that I have seen .
#Text=( ( MM ) ) Do you know of any injuries to people ?
#Text=( ( PC ) ) Yes , I know of at least 3 deaths and 5 injuries .
#Text=( ( MM ) ) Are there any details of these deaths and injuries ?
#Text=( ( PC ) ) I know a tree fell on someone 's car .
#Text=I want to add the fact transformers lit the sky up for miles .
#Text=Some for a few sec[onds ] , some for 30 [ seconds ] .
#Text=( ( MM ) ) How are emergency services responding ?
#Text=( ( PC ) ) Well I have been told that every volunteer and cop is on duty .
#Text=Also all police resources are being used from undercover cars to bikes .
#Text=( ( MM ) ) How are the telephone services and other forms of communication working ?
#Text=( ( PC ) ) There are no phone lines working . [ Wireless phones ] are the only way to communicate and ...
